{"tid":391882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教院學生恭喜蔡局長二公子獲毛主席接見","createTime":"2017-09-08T06:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T06:27:48.000Z","uid":18411,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b47848d86cf5ec78e8ddfa2c558ba032878888f4","tid":391882,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:04:57.000Z","msg":"親愛的蔡局長：<br />\n<br />\n感謝局長多年來為國家及黨盡心盡力辦事，昨日喜聞主席特此召見貴公子，本人現謹代表教院學生向局長表示最深切的祝賀。望閣下莫因此居功自傲，繼續努力為黨辦事，相信類似重賞必接踵而來。<br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n一家團聚<br />\n<br />\n教院學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/133822_75baaf3cba0b1931360e30620afba46b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F133822_75baaf3cba0b1931360e30620afba46b.jpg&h=1155ab65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">btw兩位ching我無你地咁勇，不過you will never walk alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆你個街啊張仁良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"477bad23d37c2ea4949f3bd1779d3542bef1adb2","tid":391882,"uid":53164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"舊證喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e86f7bf394bf31bb0e9e5bdee10e5f1354f4ca9","tid":391882,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"唔係副局咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81092334751d129463c33878f3c4a8846790639f","tid":391882,"uid":44243,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"屌，張圖tune光睇到樓主個柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9aa04a8d69f03b23c9b7c22cbba0f11dc164915","tid":391882,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T06:11:37.000Z","msg":"記住蒙面先貼民主牆呀<br />\n<br />\n同埋返學放學唔好用八達通"},{"pid":"98